-/**
- * vfs_path_lookup - lookup a file path relative to a dentry-vfsmount pair
- * @dentry:  pointer to dentry of the base directory
- * @mnt: pointer to vfs mount of the base directory
- * @name: pointer to file name
- * @flags: lookup flags
